#

Prosciutto and Melon Skewers with Grilled Chicken Caprese Salad

$25
450 kcal
Difficulty: 40%

Allergens:

NutsDairy

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeHigh-Protein

Tags:

AppetizerSaladGrilledGourmet

Description

A refreshing blend of sweet melon and savory prosciutto, complemented by a hearty grilled chicken salad featuring fresh mozzarella and basil.

Ingredients

  • Prosciutto: 150g
  • Cantaloupe Melon: 1 medium
  • Fresh Mozzarella: 200g
  • Fresh Basil Leaves: 1 cup
  • Cherry Tomatoes: 200g
  • Grilled Chicken Breast: 300g
  • Balsamic Glaze: to drizzle
  • Olive Oil: 2 tbsp
  • Salt: to taste
  • Black Pepper: to taste
